## 🗺️ Peta Proyek (Baca Ini Dulu)

```
BIZKITDEV/
├── .context                    ← File ini (AI rules & references)
├── docs/
│   ├── 00_INDEX.md             ← Master index & link referensi
│   ├── 01_RULES_AND_AI_AGENT.md ← Coding rules, DOD, constraints
│   ├── 02_ARCHITECTURE.md      ← Stack, API, PRD, product catalog
│   ├── 03_DATABASE_SCHEMA.md   ← SQL DDL + Drizzle schema
│   ├── 04_PIPELINE_AND_SCRIPTS.md ← GitHub Actions + AI adapter
│   ├── 05_SEO_AND_UX.md        ← SEO/AEO/GEO + design tokens
│   └── 06_DEPLOYMENT_AND_OPS.md ← Env vars, security, testing
├── config/
│   ├── brand_manifest.json     ← Target B2B Search Intent & Copy
│   ├── integration_catalog.json ← Zero-cost Integration API matrix
│   └── open_ecosystem_catalog.json ← Open source library assets
├── system_architecture.json    ← Config global (JANGAN hardcode)
├── ux_design_token.json        ← Design system tokens
├── seo_aeo_manifest.json       ← SEO/GEO configuration
├── scripts/
│   ├── agc-parser.js
│   ├── agc-engine-classifier.js
│   ├── funnel-aggregator.js     ← Automated marketing flywheel
│   └── universal-ai-adapter.js  ← Agnostic AI Refinement
└── .github/workflows/
    └── agc-pipeline-workflow.yml
```

**Stack:** Astro v4 ISR · Next.js 14 App Router · Supabase · Vercel · Cloudflare · GitHub Actions

---

## ⚡ Quick Rules (Non-Negotiable)

```
1. Baca docs/01_RULES_AND_AI_AGENT.md SEBELUM menulis kode
2. Ambil copywriting & intent dari config/brand_manifest.json
3. Semua panggilan AI → melalui scripts/universal-ai-adapter.js
4. Proses > 2.5 detik → pindah ke GitHub Actions, BUKAN Vercel
5. Setelah selesai → validasi DOD di docs/01_RULES_AND_AI_AGENT.md#3
```

