## 📐 Coding Conventions

### Naming

```typescript
// Files: kebab-case
agc-parser.js
ai-provider-adapter.js

// Variables & functions: camelCase
const itemsFetched = 0;
async function runPipeline() {}

// Types & interfaces: PascalCase
type AIResponse = { polishedTitle: string; };
interface ProductMeta { key: string; category_slug: string; }

// Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
const MAX_ITEMS_PER_RUN = 3;
```

### Import Order (Biome enforced)

```javascript
// 1. Node.js built-ins
const fs   = require('fs');
const path = require('path');

// 2. External packages
const { createClient } = require('@supabase/supabase-js');
const { GoogleGenAI }  = require('@google/generative-ai');

// 3. Internal modules
const { AIProviderAdapter }  = require('./ai-provider-adapter');
const { getProductAndRoute } = require('./agc-engine-classifier');
```

### Error Handling Pattern

```javascript
// Setiap async function di pipeline wajib:
try {
  // ... logic
} catch (error) {
  await supabase.from('automation_logs').insert([{
    items_fetched: 0,
    status: 'ERROR',
    error_details: error.message,
    execution_duration_ms: Date.now() - startTime,
  }]);
  process.exit(1);
}
```

---

## 🚫 Anti-Patterns (Jangan Lakukan)

```javascript
// ❌ Hardcode domain
<a href="https://shop.bizkitdev.com/checkout">Buy</a>

// ✅ Gunakan config
const { base_checkout_url } = sysArch.routing_architecture.fulfillment_subdomain;
<a href={`${base_checkout_url}?product_id=${productKey}`}>Buy</a>

// ❌ Instansiasi AI SDK langsung
const ai = new GoogleGenAI({ apiKey: process.env.GEMINI_API_KEY });
const result = await ai.getGenerativeModel(...);

// ✅ Gunakan adapter
const { AIProviderAdapter } = require('./ai-provider-adapter');
const adapter = new AIProviderAdapter();
const result = await adapter.polishContent(title, content);

// ❌ Proses berat di Vercel API route
export async function POST(req) {
  await crawlAndParseEntireWebsite(); // timeout!
}

// ✅ Pindah ke GitHub Actions, Vercel hanya webhook
export async function POST(req) {
  // Hanya trigger atau simpan flag
  return Response.json({ triggered: true });
}
```

---

## 📋 Definition of Done (Ringkasan)

Sebelum commit, pastikan semua checklist ini terpenuhi:

- [ ] Tidak ada domain/brand name hardcode di kode UI
- [ ] Tidak ada raw AI SDK instantiation di luar `ai-provider-adapter.js`
- [ ] Lighthouse score ≥ 95/100 (Performance, A11y, Best Practices, SEO)
- [ ] Semua halaman dinamis punya JSON-LD schema yang valid
- [ ] Biome lint & format: 0 error
- [ ] Playwright E2E test: semua checkout link verified
- [ ] (Jika ada DB change) Migration file terbuat dan tested

---

## 📞 Support & Resources

| Kebutuhan | Solusi |
|---|---|
| Supabase free tier pause | Write ke `automation_logs` setiap 48h via GitHub Actions |
| Vercel timeout | Pindah logic ke GitHub Actions runner |
| AI failover | Grok → Gemini → OpenRouter → Hardcoded (urutan di adapter) |
| Rate limit Gemini | Ganti ke OpenRouter dengan model gratis |
| Bot spam di form | Aktifkan Arcjet + Cloudflare Turnstile |
| LCP tinggi | Baca skill `debug-optimize-lcp` |
| Accessibility issue | Baca skill `a11y-debugging` |
| Kode berantakan | Jalankan `npx biome check --apply .` |

